# Termax

Termax is an LLM agent in your terminal to make your life easier.

With termax, you can

- üçº Ask Commands: ask your terminal to execute commands, no need to know them in advance.
- üìê Tailor Commands: customize and fix commands for your devices, even those copied from Stack Overflow.
- üí° Smart Hint: intelligent suggestions for your next steps.

## Installation

```bash
pip install termax
```

